{"tid":388791,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(健身撚請入）掌上壓問題","createTime":"2017-09-05T16:37:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T07:39:49.000Z","uid":19653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d9634a877a9550391a53f86d230ac8158c84af0","tid":388791,"uid":19653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:37:28.000Z","msg":"呢排開始做掌上壓<br />\n但係feel到右邊一頭肌痛 但左邊就無咩感覺<br />\n係咪我姿勢錯左？<br />\n同埋我想練胸<br />\n做3種掌上壓足唔足夠（正常、前臂貼腿、大字型）<br />\nThanks!"},{"pid":"4019209f0885ce0bc795d9e0fd4d28543f607330","tid":388791,"uid":137977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T16:39:11.000Z","msg":"唔夠 bulk唔到<br />\n買set器材自己挺舉"},{"pid":"230a439a25280d9dccd1860ca1cc092f3772365e","tid":388791,"uid":137766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:29:45.000Z","msg":"慢上慢落feel下個胸。做住闊手先"},{"pid":"4c47e096936ef1f14e8778b7fdccda208d176140","tid":388791,"uid":51561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T02:12:34.000Z","msg":"你隻手二三頭完全未適應依個訓練<br />\n<br />\n簡單d講係舊肌肉嘆慣未郁過<br />\n<br />\n一開波做你就唔識平衡兩邊肌肉未搞到咁囉<br />\n<br />\n慢上慢下慢慢黎啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好學中學生果d咩係咁chok上落，諗返起到on撚9<br />\n<br />\n冇用架，最緊要做啱動作，每個郁動都feel到主要練嘅肌肉係用緊，收放緊<br />\n<br />\n加油！唔好做季候鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4620186f3f763a13a6dd2d556520efbf1528d523","tid":388791,"uid":51561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T02:14:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔夠 bulk唔到<br />\n買set器材自己挺舉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先俾肌肉feel咗自己體重先其實算係基本功"},{"pid":"c99abe341352323a6517f473af4ec9841a58a2d0","tid":388791,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T02:28:15.000Z","msg":"有咁慢得咁慢"},{"pid":"1d9b6e523bd77096c8098d95005585ea8bc37938","tid":388791,"uid":98680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T02:30:10.000Z","msg":"一頭肌打飛機用架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9661178b439b18651f32864aa282235bc997350a","tid":388791,"uid":4527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T02:30:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔夠 bulk唔到<br />\n買set器材自己挺舉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先俾肌肉feel咗自己體重先其實算係基本功</blockquote><br />\n其實掌上壓識做都玩到成績，當然唔夠做gym快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac0ca7d02e52a9cadb5bbd0b2ec04ebdfb53c2b","tid":388791,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T02:33:58.000Z","msg":"一下都做唔到<br />\n點搞"},{"pid":"f83d193ec8ec50f897b29db851ea64f035e2a272","tid":388791,"uid":140666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T02:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢排開始做掌上壓<br />\n但係feel到右邊一頭肌痛 但左邊就無咩感覺<br />\n係咪我姿勢錯左？<br />\n同埋我想練胸<br />\n做3種掌上壓足唔足夠（正常、前臂貼腿、大字型）<br />\nThanks!</blockquote><br />\n乜係一頭肌？ 定你想講二頭or 三頭？"},{"pid":"b87e8b6bb10ecbd0db859bc075b8c4243fcc3f45","tid":388791,"uid":51561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T02:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔夠 bulk唔到<br />\n買set器材自己挺舉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先俾肌肉feel咗自己體重先其實算係基本功</blockquote><br />\n其實掌上壓識做都玩到成績，當然唔夠做gym快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基本肌力一定練到<br />\n<br />\n但個人體重唔會日日唔同架嘛，而且肌肉係有記憶架，當一定時期做慣咗同一種重量就唔會再點buff<br />\n<br />\n自己玩玩下一定會再有要求嘅，到時仲未放棄健身嘅未買器材或者去gym room囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cbc81000c30b69d26f3bd3edd9bc361f51716a0","tid":388791,"uid":51561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T02:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一下都做唔到<br />\n點搞</blockquote><br />\n雙手角度唔洗屈曬住，慢慢un落少少俾肌肉feel慣個力先<br />\n<br />\n定係唔通你想放棄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc769376949957f56563fb71c66f49b9b426b679","tid":388791,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T02:39:18.000Z","msg":"一頭肌我終於練到50寸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9af14fd95ea53374ed92b0f71b0239bcd56e38","tid":388791,"uid":51561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T02:43:57.000Z","msg":"唔好退卻<br />\n<br />\n諗住「退，懶你就輸成世，一世做肥仔」<br />\n<br />\n依句真係好有推動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359c7149a3e3e8d0d4d50676de44b51fca23e8aa","tid":388791,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T03:03:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢排開始做掌上壓<br />\n但係feel到右邊一頭肌痛 但左邊就無咩感覺<br />\n係咪我姿勢錯左？<br />\n同埋我想練胸<br />\n做3種掌上壓足唔足夠（正常、前臂貼腿、大字型）<br />\nThanks!</blockquote><br />\n乜係一頭肌？ 定你想講二頭or 三頭？</blockquote><br />\n一頭都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5587790ef4bbef555d184242366d5a135488421c","tid":388791,"uid":31408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:33:59.000Z","msg":"未慣姐 等你做多啲warmup 就ok了"},{"pid":"0d41a41e2835798c1a3443e6fdbc00caafbab1f4","tid":388791,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:39:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔夠 bulk唔到<br />\n買set器材自己挺舉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先俾肌肉feel咗自己體重先其實算係基本功</blockquote><br />\n其實掌上壓識做都玩到成績，當然唔夠做gym快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基本肌力一定練到<br />\n<br />\n但個人體重唔會日日唔同架嘛，而且肌肉係有記憶架，當一定時期做慣咗同一種重量就唔會再點buff<br />\n<br />\n自己玩玩下一定會再有要求嘅，到時仲未放棄健身嘅未買器材或者去gym room囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到口都臭，肌肉係唔知你舉緊鐵定自己體重，佢剩係識感受刺激，overload就會有增長"},{"pid":"b99d5cd995a11dbf43215a8f274515043533aaf9","tid":388791,"uid":32314,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:28:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"744fef62cb4e13987be802af51845f9219ee0bf5","tid":388791,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:30:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"h