手先"},{"pid":"9af14ee9367c6a48147ffaa2f75fd0b1d3b7756b","tid":388791,"uid":94739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T07:24:51.000Z","msg":"想問下姿勢點先標準？ 成日驚自己姿勢唔標準用錯力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d153b58be33226f189822e63e801e274166e04e","tid":388791,"uid":138071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T07:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下姿勢點先標準？ 成日驚自己姿勢唔標準用錯力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果唔夠力，膝頭跪地做(要毯毯個地) ，等夠力先做返正常掌上壓"}]}